  "original_title": "\u0d86\u0dbb\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dda\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dc0 \u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dc4\u0ddd\u0daf\u0dbb \u0daf\u0dd1\u0dad \u0daf\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dd4 \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Armenia extends brotherly arms to Sri Lanka",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The President of Armenia Mr. Vahagn Khachaturyan has stated in a congratulatory message to President Ranil Wickramasinghe that he is committed to further strengthen the cooperation between the Republic of Armenia and Sri Lanka for the benefit of the people of both countries.",
        "The President of Armenia has congratulated Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe who has been elected as the President and has appreciated the commitment of Mr. Wickramasinghe for the progress of Sri Lanka.",
        "The congratulatory message of the Armenian President further states that he wishes good health, success and peace to the friendly people of Sri Lanka."
      ],
